title: Ep. #98 | Big News! & IU, Bobby, and Hyuna!
description:
Eric returns for a part 2 to catch up and review the many comebacks of big K-pop artists! Get ready to listen to January's most exciting comebacks including: "Celebrity" by IU, "U MAD?" by BOBBY, "I'm Not Cool" by Hyuna, and more!
